  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>All Tengu pine and wish for the ability to fly, but their avian nature does help them when falling back to earth. If you are not incapacitated or wearing heavy armor (unless it is specifically made from a material that removes the Strength requirement to don), you can extend the feathers of your arms and tail and glide. When you do so, you can perform the following aerial maneuvers:</p><ul><li>You can move up to 5 feet horizontally for every 1 foot you descend in the air, at no movement cost to you; however you cannot exceed your maximum distance traveled in a turn and remain in your glide until you end it.</li><li>When you would take damage from falling, you can use your reaction to reduce the fall's damage to 0.</li></ul>",
